Texts.Chs:
一罐三文鱼（英文：salmon）。蛋白质的重要来源。大多数人认为salmon中的“l”是不发音的。但你仍然可以说成“saLmon”，并将这个“L”的音发出来。毕竟这只是一罐三文鱼。它不能因此而评判你。它只能被打开，里面的东西也只能被吃掉。
^orange;类型：熟肉食^reset;
Texts.Eng:
A can of salmon. A great source of protein. Most people think the L is silent. But you can say salmon and pronounce the L. This is a can of salmon. It can't judge you. It can only be opened, and its contents, eaten.
^orange;Type: Cooked Meat^reset;
